snippet.title: Angelic - First Official Trailer (2021 April)
snippet.description:
The first official trailer of Angelic. Angelic is a narrative strategy RPG set in a dark and collaborative sci-fi universe. 

This trailer was released in April 2021 and is based on the initial iteration of Angelic, which was in development from February 2020 to May 2021. While this iteration was never officially released, it laid the groundwork for both Angelic: Dark Symphony and Angelic: The Chaos Theatre.

For further details on the latest iterations of Angelic, please visit our official webpage: https://angelicthegame.com. 

Don't forget to wishlist us on Steam and Epic Store:

http://bit.ly/AngelicSteam
http://bit.ly/AngelicEpic

More information: 
https://linktr.ee/angelicthegame
